name: Minji - NewJeans
description:
Minji

NewJeans

This is a favor for work friend (Hey Sammy!) who asked me a million questions about SD today, and threw in that Minji is his current crush.

Minji is a member of the K-Pop group NewJeans. There's 5 girls in the group, Minji is only one of 2 who are 18, so there won't be a complete set for at least 3 years.

I got roasted for my Tzuyu embedding, so I'm sure another one is coming.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!

[ SDv1.4, 5e-03, 4400, .207 ]
